channel.title: O my god
channel.description: wow this site is still up... i dont even know where to start with scripting anymore. are scripts still efficient as they used to be? i logged into runescape earlier today for the first time in a long time and everything has changed. i mean everything from a year ago. amazing SCAR is still running. thought id stop by and see whats goin down. sucks all the work i put into scripting just means nothing now. i had messages in my inbox about my runecrafter which i forgot all about. a lot of familiar names. nashi(remember him from the very first day i started to script, he helped me a lot), freddy, etc... theres no point to this post really so dont spam you noobs hahaha. ahhhh memories.
